# 🖥️ E-commerce Sales Dashboard (Power BI)

## 📌 Objective
To build an interactive dashboard to track and analyze sales performance, regional trends, and customer behavior for an e-commerce platform.

## 🛠️ Tool Used
- Power BI

## 📊 Key Features
- Visual KPIs for Sales, Profit, and Orders
- Region-wise and category-wise filtering
- Customer segment performance
- Trend analysis with slicers and drill-down capabilities

## 📌 Insights
- Identified high-performing regions and underperforming categories
- Helped visualize seasonal sales trends and product demand patterns

## 🧑‍💻 About Me
I created this dashboard to strengthen my Power BI skills and demonstrate my ability to communicate data-driven insights visually.
